{"tid":2246362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人發覺食肆待應戴膠手套係一件好嘔心嘅事？","createTime":"2020-10-17T03:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T04:57:53.000Z","uid":141100,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"efdd956a620c42c9b4fa2dae4478b2d4512bcd5a","tid":2246362,"uid":141100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:56:30.000Z","msg":"近呢一年 因為疫情關係好多食肆樓面都會戴左膠手套做野<br />\n我明白佢地咁樣做係出於保護自己 但我唔相信佢地會成日換手套/戴住手套洗手<br />\n我估佢地執枱執人食完啲野找錢 甚至乎洗廁所執垃圾都係個隻手套而且唔會清潔 跟手又拎野食同包外賣比你 其實真係好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086fbf37389a815183e22ec207158eadf6c2a6d7","tid":2246362,"uid":143016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:58:08.000Z","msg":"不嬲戴膠手都污糟 無論係廚師同待應 不過d 客覺得乾淨 由尻佢"},{"pid":"978d33dcc17ccda8897a0724def825dbd600abaf","tid":2246362,"uid":284304,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"真 飲食業帶手套完全係自欺欺人"},{"pid":"ddc7e49cfb2d380f65bc35252d48eeaaad870016","tid":2246362,"uid":167277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"覺得 超核突<br />\n得佢地自己感覺良好 以為自己好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd藍色手套黑晒嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832832090fcab709d18e7fde1d167d24f23d36f0","tid":2246362,"uid":353482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"壽司佬放完水唔洗手添"},{"pid":"0a31343238e6dc68939a6709ca67aa2adfc3040d","tid":2246362,"uid":59501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"入面出撚哂汗<br />\n焗撚到生野<br />\n唔戴又比閪客屌<br />\n戴又話核突<br />\n有得揀人地好想戴咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b427712d2caa1ff2622a748e7223557584a80f9b","tid":2246362,"uid":358288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"袁國勇一早講咗，佢哋對萬能膠手套最容易造成交差感染。<br />\n<br />\n上次去燒山餐廳食嘢，嗰個明明心口有個牌掛住「執枱員」，照樣送餐，攞餐具俾你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf90838d0361bf693df52836d2848f8ae26ecf1","tid":2246362,"uid":125017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"個手套其實係用黎保護個待應對手<br />\n可想而知街外D野食幾烏糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bbd8902c9b67b4b4b3a4931c0a6b4243bcc52a","tid":2246362,"uid":292416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"早幾日去食雲吞河，廚房阿叔裸手俾碗麵我，見唔慣但好安心"}]}